They're threatening to
kick him out of school.

51:05.864 --> 51:07.298
-- The Confederate flag?
-- Yeah.

51:07.365 --> 51:09.197
They fly the flag
outside the stadium?

51:09.267 --> 51:11.395
-- Yeah. -- <i>Also, students
wave 'em in the stands.</i>

51:11.469 --> 51:13.164
Nothing you can do
about that.

51:13.238 --> 51:15.206
Yeah, but outside the
stadium, that's the school.

51:15.273 --> 51:17.002
<i>Anyway, there'll be
a press conference at 3:00.</i>

51:17.075 --> 51:18.736
We have it on satellite.

51:18.810 --> 51:21.643
The rumor is Roland won't play unless
the school takes the flag down.

51:21.713 --> 51:24.546
<i>The school's gonna announce that
Roland is suspended from the team,</i>

51:24.616 --> 51:26.710
as a result of which his
scholarship will be revoked,

51:26.785 --> 51:28.446
as a result of which
Roland will go back

51:28.520 --> 51:30.989
and pump gas
in Tipolo, Tennessee.

51:31.056 --> 51:33.821
Dan, be on
the press conference.

51:33.892 --> 51:37.226
<i>Meantime, I need to hear some plays
of the year by the end of the day.</i>

51:37.295 --> 51:38.353
Thank you.

51:38.430 --> 51:40.159
Back here at 6:00.

51:40.231 --> 51:41.960
Danny, I need
to talk to you.

51:42.033 --> 51:44.934
