52:09.994 --> 52:11.826
A piece on
Southern gentlemen,

52:11.896 --> 52:13.295
the Southern tradition --

52:13.365 --> 52:15.390
the Southern tradition
in sports,

52:15.467 --> 52:16.935
in culture, in history.

52:17.001 --> 52:20.027
-- All symbolized by the Confederate flag.
-- You learn <i>fast.</i>

52:20.105 --> 52:21.436
-- <i>You really want to do this?</i>
