I-| don't know.

54:05.844 --> 54:07.471
No, you don't.

54:07.545 --> 54:09.377
There's no reason
why you should.

54:09.447 --> 54:12.849
You're not expected to know
what shirt goes with what suit

54:12.917 --> 54:15.943
or how a color in a necktie
can pick up your eyes.

54:16.020 --> 54:17.579
You're not expected to
know what --

54:17.655 --> 54:19.555
what's gonna clash
with what Dan's wearing

54:19.624 --> 54:23.219
or what pattern's gonna bleed
when Dave changes the lighting.

54:23.294 --> 54:26.662
Mr. McCall, you get so much
attention and so much praise

54:26.731 --> 54:29.723
