complimented on something you didn't,

54:35.507 --> 54:37.874
how hard would it be
to say, "That's not me.

54:37.942 --> 54:41.936
“That's a woman named Maureen who's been
working for us since the first day.

54:42.013 --> 54:44.812
"It's Maureen who
dresses me every night,

54:44.883 --> 54:48.581
