for her husband and her kids?

55:03.701 --> 55:05.760
I know --

55:05.837 --> 55:09.603
I know this is when it
starts to get busy for you.

55:09.674 --> 55:12.974
I hope I didn't take up
too much of your time.

55:13.044 --> 55:14.136
<i>[ Exhales deeply]</i>

55:14.212 --> 55:16.772
<i>Please don't tell
Maureen I spoke to you.</i>

55:16.848 --> 55:18.577
